T1  - Teams Make You Smarter: How Exposure to Teams Improves Individual Decisions in Probability and Reasoning Tasks
AU  - Maciejovsky, Boris
AU  - Sutter, Matthias
AU  - Budescu, David V.
AU  - Bernau, Patrick
Y1  - 2013/01/08
PY  - 2013
DA  - 2013/06/01
